Quickest way to create 'hello world' web app in Java (< 5 minutes)

New maven project based on the maven webapp archetype (maven-archetype-webapp)

Add Tomcat to build section of POM:
    <build>
        <pluginManagement>
            <plugins>
                <plugin>
                    <groupId>org.apache.tomcat.maven</groupId>
                    <artifactId>tomcat7-maven-plugin</artifactId>
                    <version>2.2</version>
                    <configuration>
                        <path>/</path>
                        <contextReloadable>true</contextReloadable>
                    </configuration>
                </plugin>
            </plugins>
        </pluginManagement>
    </build>

Create run configuration with command line argument of 'tomcat7:run'
